snippet.title: Willy Morgan coming to Nintendo Switch!
snippet.description: Willy Morgan is a point and click adventure game, set in a pirate themed fantasy world with a modern twist. Explore an unconventional pirate town, investigate the past, collect items and look for clues to help Willy find out what happened to his father. Available in Q1 2021 on Nintendo Switch.
